data.description: Did someone say PRIVATE COURT YARD?  Look no further, 103 River Chase Court has what you are looking for and maybe some things you didn't know you wanted!!!  LIVING SPACES, OUTDOOR SPACES, CLOSET SPACES....There is space for you to create tons of memories for you and your family.  Once entering the home off the foyer to the right there are 2 guest bedrooms which share a full bath.  To the left of the foyer is a great space currently used as an office.  Adjacent to the office space is the kitchen featuring a lot of counter space, plenty of cabinets, ample sized pantry, granite island, and a breakfast bar. In addition to the breakfast area there is a formal dining room. The main suite is tucked away from the guest bedrooms.  It offers 2 walk-in closets, a garden tub, shower and double split vanities!  The laundry room has plenty of cabinets for storage and a sink! Upstairs is a large recreational room and kitchenette style room with space for a full-sized refrigerator, a sink, and cabinets.  Also, upstairs are 2 spacious guest bedrooms. Could there be more? Yes of course there is more......An enclosed sunroom with an attached storage, garage with workshop and storage space and the back yard is fenced in for PRIVACY!!! If you need extra storage in your next home......103 River Chase Court is for you.  If you need functional spaces for entertaining, 103 River Chase Court is for you.  If you space to retreat for a private yoga session or a game day extravaganza, 103 River Chase Court is for you. Schedule your appointment today!!
